scheduled_maintenances.name: [GRA1][Dedicated Servers] - Racks G114B24 - G114B21 network equipment maintenance notification

incident_updates.body: As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our network infrastructure in the specific racks G114B24 - G114B21. Start time : 08/10/2025 00:00 UTC End time : 08/10/2025 02:00 UTC Service impact : Public and vRack network will be temporarily unavailable during the maintenance. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy of our network infrastructure, we will have to carry out interventions on multiple network equipment in racks G114B24 and G114B21. Thank you for your understanding.

As part of our continuous improvement plan, maintenance is scheduled on our Dedicated Servers offer. This may temporarily affect availability. Start time : 09/10/2025 00:00 UTC End time : 09/10/2025 02:00 UTC Service impact : During the maintenance window, the public network will be unavailable. Please note that the maintenance may take less time than expected. Service improvement : As part of our continuous improvement policy, we will be doing a maintenance on our network equipment. Thank you for your understanding.
